3. Java program to display all integers within the range 100-150 whose sum of digits
is an even number
Ans.3 public class sum_even {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
	int r;
	int n;
	for(int i=100; i<=150;i++)
	{
		int sum=0;
		n=i;
		while(n!=0) {
		r = n%10;
		n= n/10;
		sum+= r;
		}
		if(sum%2==0)
			System.out.println(i);
	}	
	}

}

